  "instructions": [
    "1. In a large bowl, whisk together fermented lime juice, cumin, paprika, garlic powder, salt, and pepper.",
    "2. Add the chicken pieces to the marinade and mix until coated. Cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
